OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FThe government has been forced to
OL,7,Ftrigger an emergency plan to deal with
OL,8,Fovercrowding in England's jails, as
OL,9,FITV News Political Correspondent Carl
OL,10,FDinnen reports
OL,12,FAn emergency plan has been triggered
OL,13,Fby the government to ease overcrowding
OL,14,Fin which could mean some court
OL,15,Fhearings are delayed.
OL,17,FThe mechanism, called Operation Early
OL,18,FDawn, is expected to be in action for
OL,19,Fa week.
