OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FThe measure is a long-standing
OL,7,Fcontingency plan, and allows
OL,8,Fdefendants to be held in police cells
OL,9,Funtil prison beds become available,
OL,10,Fbut could mean their court dates are
OL,11,Fdelayed or adjourned.
OL,13,FIt allows the prison service to make
OL,14,Fjudgements each morning on whether
OL,15,Fprisoners are taken to courts or
OL,16,Fremain in police cells.
