OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FJustice officials are yet to confirm
OL,7,Fhow many cases will be affected but
OL,8,Fstressed the measures, while rolled
OL,9,Fout across England, do not mean there
OL,10,Fwill be delays in every region and
OL,11,Finsisted the plan was put in place to
OL,12,Flimit disruption.
OL,14,FITV News understands the current
OL,15,Flocations where the plan is being
OL,16,Factivated are London and the North
OL,17,FEast.
