OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice said: "We
OL,7,Fcontinue to see pressure on our
OL,8,Fprisons following the impact of the
OL,9,Fpandemic and barristers' strike which
OL,10,Fis why we have initiated a previously
OL,11,Fused measure to securely transfer
OL,12,Fprisoners between courts and custody
OL,13,Fand ensure there is always a custody
OL,14,Fcell available should they be
OL,15,Fremanded."
OL,17,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,18,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,19,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,20,Fdominating the political agenda...
