OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FThe move has raised questions as to
OL,7,Fwhether defendants who would normally
OL,8,Fbe held in custody on remand while
OL,9,Ftheir case moves through the courts
OL,10,Fmay have to be initially released on
OL,11,Fbail. Although the government said
OL,12,Fcourts and police are not being
OL,13,Finstructed to do so.
OL,15,FIt comes as Sir Keir Starmer urged
OL,16,FRishi Sunak to stop trying to issue
OL,17,F"get out of jail free cards" to
OL,18,Fcriminals during Prime Minister's
OL,19,FQuestions, comparing the Prime
OL,20,FMinister to a "jumped-up milk monitor".
