OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FThe Labour leader referenced another
OL,7,Fgovernment scheme which allows some
OL,8,Flow-level offenders to be released
OL,9,Fearly, and is due to be extended from
OL,10,Fnext week to allow sentences to be cut
OL,11,Fby up to 70 days.
OL,13,FSir Keir accused the Tory government
OL,14,Fof causing "chaos" in the prison
OL,15,Fsystem, asking "does the prime
OL,16,Fminister think that his decision to
OL,17,Fallow prisoners out 70 days early
OL,18,Fmakes our country more secure?"
