OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FThe government's End of Custody
OL,7,FSupervised License Scheme (ECSL)
OL,8,Finitially involved inmates being
OL,9,Freleased up to 18 days early. That was
OL,10,Fthen , and will be further extended to
OL,11,F70 days from 23 May.
OL,13,FA row broke out during PMQs over
OL,14,Fwhether prisoners who are considered
OL,15,Fhigh risk will be released under the
OL,16,Fscheme, after a report from the
OL,17,Fprison's inspector said high risk
OL,18,Foffenders including a domestic abuser
OL,19,Fwho posed a risk to children had been
OL,20,Freleased.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/13
