OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FCharlie Taylor's report said he had
OL,7,F"serious concerns" about the early
OL,8,Frelease scheme, citing an inmate at
OL,9,FHMP Lewes who posed a danger to
OL,10,Fchildren having his release date
OL,11,Fbrought forward.
OL,13,FIn light of this report, Sir Keir
OL,14,Fpressed the PM for assurance on
OL,15,Fwhether the prisoners being let out
OL,16,Fearly are "considered to be high risk."
