OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FMr Sunak responded by saying: "Let me
OL,7,Fbe crystal clear, no-one would be put
OL,8,Fon the scheme if they were deemed a
OL,9,Fthreat to the public. Offenders are
OL,10,Fsubject to the toughest of licensing
OL,11,Fconditions, and if those conditions
OL,12,Fare broken, they are back in prison
OL,13,Ffor considerably longer."
OL,15,FBut there are significant concerns
OL,16,Fthat people convicted of domestic
OL,17,Fviolence are being released under the
OL,18,Fscheme.
