OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FAbigail Ampofo CEO of the domestic
OL,7,Fviolence charity Refuge said this
OL,8,Fannouncement was a "disappointing
OL,9,Fsuprise" and will have a "huge impact"
OL,10,Fon survivors of domestic abuse.
OL,12,F"One of the things we know is domestic
OL,13,Fabuse is poorly understood, it's not
OL,14,Fneccessarily the easiest crime to be
OL,15,Fable to achieve a prosecution for, and
OL,16,Fnot knowing when your perpetrator is
OL,17,Fgoing to be released not only puts you
OL,18,Fat physical risk, but there's a huge
OL,19,Famount of psychological concern and
OL,20,Flack of safety."
