OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FThe Labour leader criticised the PM
OL,7,Ffor focusing too much on, rather than
OL,8,Fon issues like the "prison system in
OL,9,Fchaos".
OL,11,FThe government blame overcrowding in
OL,12,FUK jails on pressures during the
OL,13,Fpandemic and industrial action by
OL,14,Fbarristers in 2022. But prisons
OL,15,Fwatchdog Charlie Taylor has branded
OL,16,Fthe situation "entirely predictable".
OL,18,F"The criminal justice system is in
OL,19,Fcrisis": Law Society say
